<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Turtle Shelter Project</title>
    <link rel="icon"  type="image/png" href="/images/logo.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/general.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
      /* About Wrapper */
/* About Section */
.about-wrapper {
    max-width: 1100px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: left;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 0 auto; /* Centers the container horizontally */
}

/* Make the About Us text above the image */
.about-content {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-top: 20px;
}

/* Image Styling */
.about-image {
    max-width: 40%; /* Adjust size as needed */
    height: auto;
    margin-left: 20px;
}

/* About Us Text Styling */
.about-wrapper p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #333;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 55%;
    margin-top: 0;
}

.about-wrapper h1 {
    font-size: 75px;
    color: #16a085;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 55%;
    margin-top: 0;
    text-align: center;
    padding-left: 220px;
}

.about-wrapper h2 {
  font-size: 24px;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.about-wrapper h3 {
  font-size: 20px;
  color: #444;
  margin-bottom: 15px;
  font-weight: normal;
}

.about-wrapper .about-text {
  flex: 2; /* Make the text section take up more space */
}

.about-wrapper .about-image {
  flex: 1; /* The image will take up 1/3 of the space in the flex container */
  max-width: 400px; /* Limit the image width */
  height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
  border-radius: 8px; /* Slightly round corners */
  box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); /* Add subtle shadow */
  object-fit: contain; /* Ensure the image doesn't distort */
}


/* Counter Wrapper */
.counter-wrapper {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  margin-top: 40px; /* Add some space above the counter section */
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.counter-content {
  text-align: center;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(10px);
  animation: fade-in 1.2s ease-out forwards;
}

.counter-number {
  font-size: 12rem;
  font-weight: bold;
  color: #16a085;
  margin: 0;
}

.impact-text {
  font-size: 18px;
  color: #333;
  margin-top: 15px;
  line-height: 1.5;
  max-width: 500px;
  text-align: center;
}

.counter-wrapper h2 {
  margin-top: 10px;
  font-size: 30px;
  color: #444;
}


/* Fade-in Animation */
@keyframes fade-in {
  0% {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
  }
  100% {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}

/* Footer Styles */
.footer {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    background-color: #454545; /* Set background color */
    color: white; /* Text color */
    padding: 20px 0; /* Padding for spacing */
    text-align: center; /* Center-align the text */
    font-size: 14px; /* Adjust text size */
}

.footer a {
    color: #f1f1f1; /* Light color for links */
    text-decoration: none; /* Remove underline */
}

.footer a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline; /* Underline on hover */
}


    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
      <%- include('partials/navbar.ejs') %>
    </header>
    <main class="intro">
      <h2>Helping to save lives of people experiencing homelessness</h2>
      <h1>STARTS WITH YOU</h1><br>
      <ul class="intro-buttons">
          <li><a href="/youhelp/donate"><button>DONATE NOW</button></a></li>
          <li><a href="/about"><button>LEARN MORE</button></a></li>
      </ul>
  </main>
  <div class="about-wrapper">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <div class="about-content">
        <img src="/images/making.jpg" alt="Turtle Shelter Vest" class="about-image">
        <p>
            A high-tech but simple solution to help save lives - a portable "shelter" you can carry with you, just like a turtle...and YOU can help!<br> 
            <br>One winter when Jen was homeless, 7 of her friends froze to death. Jen is no longer homeless and has figured out a solution: 
            high-tech foam vests that are inexpensive, keep a person warm to 10 degrees below zero, help SAVE lives, and alleviate suffering.<br> 
            <br>YOU can request vests for your community - and you can make vests and have your friends, business colleagues, church members, or club make vests, too!
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="counter-wrapper">
    <div class="counter-content">
        <h1 class="counter-number"><%= vestCount || 5900 %></h1>
        <h2>vests distributed</h2>
        <p class="impact-text">
            Our Turtle Shelter initiative has distributed thousands of vests, 
            providing warmth and safety for people in need. Your support has made 
            this incredible impact possible.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-content">
      <p>Turtle Shelter Project, PO Box 382, Kaysville, UT 84037</p>
      <p>Phone: 801-872-3190</p>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:turtleshelterproject@gmail.com">turtleshelterproject@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>
</footer>
<script src="/scripts/script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>